eorgia (U.S. state)|Georgia]]\n| ''9''\n| '''3'''\n| {{sort|1|[[Atlanta Falcons|Falcons]]}}\n| {{sort|1|[[Atlanta Braves|Braves]]}}\n| {{sort|1|[[Atlanta Hawks|Hawks]]}}\n| align=center|{{sort|0|\u2014}}\n| '''4'''\n| {{sort|1|[[Atlanta United FC|United FC]]}}\n| align=center|{{sort|0|\u2014}}\n|-\n| {{flagicon|USA}} [[Tennessee]]\n| ''19''\n| '''3'''\n| {{sort|1|[[Tennessee Titans|Titans]]}}\n| align=center|{{sort|0|\u2014}}\n| {{sort|1|[[Memphis Grizzlies|Grizzlies]]}}\n| {{sort|1|[[Nashville Predators|Predators]]}}\n| '''4'''\n| {{sort|1|[[Nashville SC (MLS)|Nashville SC]]}}\n| align=center|{{sort|0|\u2014}}\n|-\n| {{flagicon|USA}} [[Maryland]]\n| ''21''\n| '''3'''\n| {{sort|2|[[Baltimore Ravens|Ravens]]<br>[[Washington Redskins|Redskins]]{{#tag:ref||name=NFLMD|group=note}}}}\n| {{sort|1|[[Baltimore Orioles|Orioles]]}}\n| align=center|{{sort|0|\u2014}} \n| align=center|{{sort|0|\u2014}} \n| '''3'''\n| align=center|{{sort|0|\u2014}} \n| align=center|{{sort|0|\u2014}}\n|-\n| {{flagicon|USA}} [[North Carolina]]\n| ''10''\n| '''3'''\n| {{sort|1|[[Carolina Panthers|Panthers]]}}\n| align=center|{{sort|0|\u2014}}\n| {{sort|1|[[Charlotte Hornets|Hornets]]}}\n| {{sort|1|[[Carolina Hurricanes|Hurricanes]]}}\n| '''3'''\n| align=center | {{sort|0|\u2014{{refn|group=note|A [[Charlotte MLS team]] will join MLS in 2021.}}}}\n| align=center|{{sort|0|\u2014}}\n|-\n| {{flagicon|USA}} [[Wisconsin]]\n| ''22''\n| '''3'''\n| {{sort|1|[[Green Bay Packers|Packers]]}}\n| {{sort|1|[[Milwaukee Brewers|Brewers]]}}\n| {{sort|1|[[Milwaukee Bucks|Bucks]]}}\n| align=center|{{sort|0|\u2014}}\n| '''3'''\n| align=center|{{sort|0|\u2014}}\n| align=center|{{sort|0|\u2014}}\n|-\n| {{flagicon|CAN}} [[Alberta]]\n| ''30''\n| '''2'''\n| align=center|{{sort|0|\u2014}}\n| align=center|{{sort|0|\u2014}}\n| align=center|{{sort|0|\u2014}}\n| {{sort|2|[[Calgary Flames|Flames]]<br>[[Edmonton Oilers|Oilers]]}}\n| '''4'''\n| align=center|{{sort|0|\u2014}}\n| {{sort|2|[[Calgary Stampeders|Stampeders]]<br>[[Edmonto